5. CONSISTENCY: MUST match slides 1 and 2 style EXACTLY - same colors, effects, composition

=== DO NOT ===
- Do NOT add any text other than the headline
- Do NOT modify the MSI logo
- Do NOT change the visual style from previous slides`;

return [{ json: { done: false, slide_num: 3, headline: next.headline, subtext: next.subtext || '', prompt: prompt, logo: prev.logo, remaining_slides: prev.remaining_slides.slice(1), total: prev.total, style: prev.style, topic: prev.topic, ac: prev.ac, dc: prev.dc, results: results } }];

